CTest Script variable: \fBCTEST_LABELS_FOR_SUBPROJECTS\fP \%<#\:variable:CTEST_LABELS_FOR_SUBPROJECTS>
.IP \(bu 2
\fBCTest\fP \%<#\:module:CTest> module variable: \fBCTEST_LABELS_FOR_SUBPROJECTS\fP
.UNINDENT
.sp
See Label and Subproject Summary\&.
.TP
.B \fBMakeCommand\fP
Command\-line to launch the software build process.
It will be executed in the location specified by the
\fBBuildDirectory\fP setting.
