.IP \(bu 2
CTest Script variable: \fBCTEST_BUILD_COMMAND\fP \%<#\:variable:CTEST_BUILD_COMMAND>
.IP \(bu 2
\fBCTest\fP \%<#\:module:CTest> module variable: \fBMAKECOMMAND\fP,
